snippet.title: AZZARO POUR HOMME NIGHT TIME - HOLIDAY SCENT? | FRAGRANCE REVIEW
snippet.description:
Videodex of Contents

General Fragrance Vibe:     01:32
Music & Fragrance Relationship: 02:08
Notes & Accords:      05:38
Open:               07:25
Mid:               07:37

HELLO EVERYONE! Today at StudioScents I'm talking about Azzaro Pour Homme Night Time! Is there something holiday-worthy in this green, woodsy fougere? Also discussed is the connection between music theory and fragrance! Check out my review to see what my thoughts on both are.

Thank you so much for stopping by and watching! 

Have a fantastic day, and as always - like, subscribe and comment below!

Tommy
